{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[G]How's the weather back in [C]Tennessee
[G]This time of year I bet those hills are green
[E7]And those nights out on old [D7]Hickory
[G]Are they as pretty as they used to be
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
[C]Is that old moon shining through the trees
[G]Like it used to when you still loved me
[E7]Well does it ever warm your [D7]memories
[C]So how's the weather back in Tennessee
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 3}
